name: Pasta Carbonara
ingredients: Pasta, Eggs, Bacon, Parmesan Cheese, Black Pepper
instructions: 1. Cook pasta. 2. Fry bacon. 3. Mix eggs and cheese. 4. Combine all ingredients.

name: Chicken Tikka Masala
ingredients: Chicken, Yogurt, Tomato, Cream, Garam Masala, Ginger, Garlic
instructions: 1. Marinate chicken in yogurt and spices. 2. Grill chicken. 3. Prepare sauce with tomatoes and cream. 4. Combine chicken with sauce.

name: Vegetable Stir Fry
ingredients: Mixed Vegetables, Soy Sauce, Ginger, Garlic, Sesame Oil, Rice
instructions: 1. Prepare vegetables. 2. Heat oil in wok. 3. Add garlic and ginger. 4. Add vegetables and stir fry. 5. Add soy sauce. 6. Serve with rice.

name: Beef Tacos
ingredients: Ground Beef, Taco Shells, Lettuce, Tomatoes, Cheese, Sour Cream, Taco Seasoning
instructions: 1. Brown ground beef with seasoning. 2. Warm taco shells. 3. Fill shells with beef. 4. Add toppings.

name: Chocolate Chip Cookies
ingredients: Flour, Butter, Sugar, Brown Sugar, Eggs, Vanilla Extract, Baking Soda, Salt, Chocolate Chips
instructions: 1. Preheat oven to 375F. 2. Mix butter and sugars. 3. Add eggs and vanilla. 4. Combine dry ingredients. 5. Mix wet and dry ingredients. 6. Add chocolate chips. 7. Bake for 9-11 minutes.

name: Caesar Salad
ingredients: Romaine Lettuce, Croutons, Parmesan Cheese, Caesar Dressing, Chicken Breast
instructions: 1. Wash and chop lettuce. 2. Grill chicken breast. 3. Slice chicken. 4. Toss lettuce with dressing. 5. Top with chicken, croutons, and parmesan.
